summary: An ordinance providing for the laying off, opening, widening, extending and establishing of Roxbury Street between Lindsay Place and 51st Avenue South and for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor; for the establishment of curb grades of said street between said limits; for the making of the necessary slopes for cuts and fills upon the property abutting; for the acquisition of adjacent land and other property for general municipal purposes, and providing for payment from the City Street Fund.
